        </item>
        <item>
            <title>華為發表原生智能 Harmony Intelligence   官方：首次將 AI 能力深度融入系統</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=harmony-intelligence</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 07:00:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Harmony Intelligence]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HarmonyOS NEXT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[華為]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1245204</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 2024 年華為開發者大會上，華為推出全新 HarmonyOS NEXT 操作系統，華為表示，這款操作系統的內核已經超越 Linux 內核，並首度將 AI 能力深度融入系統，為用户帶來前所未有的智能體驗。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245205 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191058-694x303.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="303" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191058-694x303.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191058.jpg 1194w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245206 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191102-694x334.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="334" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191102-694x334.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191102.jpg 1114w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="mceTemp"></div><div class="mceTemp"></div><p>華為終端 BG 軟件部總裁龔體在演講中介紹 HarmonyOS NEXT 的創新功能之一，是將 AI 能力深度整合進系統中。這次發佈的 AI 功能包括 AIGC 圖像生成，如手繪線稿、填色、塗鴉和照片擴圖等，還有業界首創的 AI 聲音修復功能，專為協助言語障礙人羣設計。此外，內置「小藝看世界」功能，可以幫助視障用户「讀圖」，例如朗讀冰箱裡的蔬菜種類、放置位置及新鮮程度。</p><p>「小藝智慧助手」也在此次大會上進行了重大升級，成為基於盤古大模型 5.0 的「小藝智能體」。用户無需喚醒助手，只需將內容拖放到手機畫面導航列上即可隨時召喚，並完成一系列操作，例如生成圖表或文本摘要。這些 AI 能力大幅提升了用户的便利性和操作效率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191128-694x269.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="269" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191128-694x269.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191128.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191107-694x328.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="328" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191107-694x328.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191107.jpg 1104w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245208" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191113-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191113-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191113.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>HarmonyOS NEXT 內置的「控件 AI 化」特性，允許第三方應用程式調用系統空間，實現實時朗讀、智能填充、圖文翻譯和主體摳圖等功能。這些創新功能將極大地提升用户體驗，使操作更加直觀便捷。</p><p>華為表示，HarmonyOS NEXT 將於 8 月推送普通消費者專用的 Beta 版本。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/776/780.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmonyos-next-7/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為：HarmonyOS NEXT 打破歐美壟斷，已超越 Linux 內核性能升 10.7% 更流暢更安全</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/dnf-removed-from-some-android-application-store/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">騰訊手遊 DNF 疑因遊戲分傭矛盾　下架華為、OPPO、VIVO 等 Android 商店平台</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/18/harmonyosnext-removed-all-source-code-from-us/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">外媒：華為 HarmonyOS NEXT　將刪除與美國有關的所有原始程式碼</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/">華為發表原生智能 Harmony Intelligence   官方：首次將 AI 能力深度融入系統</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
