            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>雖然 2018 年上映的機動戰士高達 NT，評價並不太怎麼樣，表現算是中規中矩，但 Bandai 是不會放過任何搶錢的機會的，今次推出的 MG，就是劇中的敍述高達 C 裝備，亦有三文魚高達之稱，到達會否有什麼新驚喜呢？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8931-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8931-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8931.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>將近 6 年後，Bandai 終於推出了敍述高達的 KA 版 MG 模型，定價為 7,700 日圓（含税）。由於 NT 高達本體的裝備實不多，零件板件量是較少的，大多數的版件都是骨架的組成。其紅色的精神框架，是與獨角獸高達的骨架配色極為相似，而今次 NT 高達的精神框架就是在紋理處理方面更為優勝，觀感更有睇頭，更可以用紫外光燈照射時，有特別亮眼的效果。另外亦提供了 MG 獨角獸的精神框架，不過卻是灰色的，可以還原未啟動狀態，不過小編來看就不會用此灰色的精神框架了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245247" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8086-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8086-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8086.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8087-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8087-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8087.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8088-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8088-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8088.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8089-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8089-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8089.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8084-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8084-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8084.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8090-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8090-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8090.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>説明書方面，新增了組裝每個部位時所需要的板件，一目瞭然非常清楚，而敍述高達的內構部分表現也很出色，手腿部分大量暴露內構，拆除外部裝甲即可看到內構的各項細節。而紅色的精神框架部分安裝在骨架框架和外甲上，使內構形態更完整充實。由於涉及 C 裝備的設計，整體結構比預期複雜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8096-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8096-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8096.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8092-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8092-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8092.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>外觀細節方面加入了不少 KA 版設計，例如胸口凸起結構和外甲邊緣的分色細節，外觀非常之有特色，當然 KA 版就一定有 KA 版的專有大量水貼，雖然是水貼地獄，但花點時間貼好後，是非常之靚仔的，這亦是小編一向都很喜愛 KA 版的原因之一。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8413-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8413-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8413.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8121-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8121-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8121.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8122-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8122-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8122.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8140-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8140-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8140.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8141-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8141-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8141.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8165-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8165-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8165.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8288-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8288-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8288.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8300-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8300-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8300.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245264" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8302-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8302-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8302.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8412-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8412-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8412.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>核心戰機造型別緻，駕駛艙細節豐富，變形流程相當複雜，腰部和手腿關節需要小心調整，否則容易出現磨損和脱扣情況。外觀細節在 MG 化後更加清晰，雙 V 型天線和頭頂黑色砲口的火神砲細節鋭利。胸部設計方面，駕駛艙門可獨立展開，腰部可動受到核心戰機影響有所限制，手臂和腿部可動性高，手指關節靈活。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8289-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8289-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8289.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8109-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8109-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8109.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-wi